<div id="pf4d" class="pf wc hd" data-page-no="4d"><div class="pc pc4d wc hd"><img class="bi x0 y0 wd he" alt="" src="bg4d.png"/><div class="t m78d x24 h19 ya39 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;We know that in everything God </div><div class="t m78e x52 h19 ya3a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">works for good with those who love </div><div class="t m3d6 x52 h19 ya3b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">him&quot; (Rom. 8:28, RSV). </div><div class="t m78f xd9 h17 ya3c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The book of Job does not provide a </div><div class="t m790 x52 h17 ya3d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">complete answer to the problem of </div><div class="t m78d x52 h17 ya3e ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pain. Job&apos;s experience shows why and </div><div class="t m39b x52 h17 y179 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">how one man suffered, and how God </div><div class="t m791 x52 h17 y69 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eventually revealed Himself to the </div><div class="t m53e x52 h17 y17a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sufferer and reversed his fortunes. It </div><div class="t m792 x52 h17 y17b ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cannot be concluded that every </div><div class="t m793 x52 h17 ya6 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">person who suffers is an actor in a </div><div class="t m794 x52 h17 y17d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">divine drama as was Job. </div><div class="t m51a xd9 h17 ya8 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Most of </div><div class="t m795 x63 h17 ya3f ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our </div><div class="t m796 x7f h17 ya40 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">headaches and </div><div class="t m797 x52 h17 ya9 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heartaches result from the normal </div><div class="t m798 x52 h17 yaa ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hazards of life in this world. We bring </div><div class="t m677 x52 h17 yab ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disease on ourselves by not paying </div><div class="t m799 x52 h17 yac ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">attention to the laws of life and health. </div><div class="t m79a x52 h17 yad ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We are all potential victims of </div><div class="t m79b x52 h17 yaf ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accident, viruses, disappointments, </div><div class="t m79c x52 h17 yb1 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">losses, and many other </div><div class="t m194 x30 h19 y759 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 10 August 31 to September 6 </div><div class="t m79d x28 h2c y75a ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Berra</div><div class="t m79e xce h2c y171 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m79f x88 h2c y171 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">n </div><div class="t m6cf x93 h17 y238 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pain-producing factors. </div><div class="t m348 x58 h17 y562 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">From Job we can learn of God&apos;s love </div><div class="t m608 x93 h17 y65 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for and patience with the sufferer. We </div><div class="t m7a0 x93 h17 y563 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">can learn how &quot;God works for good </div><div class="t m5c5 x93 h17 y9f9 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with those who love him.&quot; But in many </div><div class="t m558 x93 h17 ya41 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">respects Job&apos;s experience was not </div><div class="t m7a1 x93 h17 y58f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">typical of everyday human life. The </div><div class="t m7a2 x93 h17 y1de ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">purpose of this lesson is to stress the </div><div class="t m7a3 x93 h17 ya42 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">truth that the same God who helped </div><div class="t m7a4 x93 h17 y566 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job resolve his problems will help us </div><div class="t m7a5 x93 h17 y567 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;in everything.&quot; God is concerned </div><div class="t m7a6 x93 h17 y568 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">about all kinds of pain, physical and </div><div class="t m7a7 x93 h17 y569 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mental. He looks with compassion on </div><div class="t m7a8 x93 h17 y1e3 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the father, worried about how to pay </div><div class="t m7a9 x93 h17 ya43 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the bills, and the mother, concerned </div><div class="t m555 x93 h17 ya44 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">about the bringing up of her children. </div><div class="t m7aa x93 h17 y37 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He feels the pain of the cancer patient </div><div class="t m18a x93 h17 y241 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the heartache of the bereaved. He </div><div class="t m28d x93 h17 y56a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">does not promise to exempt us from </div><div class="t m7ab x93 h17 y56b ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">all these hazards as long as we are in </div><div class="t m1bb x93 h17 y56c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the world. We must accept our lot as </div><div class="t m6d0 x93 h17 y56d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fellow sufferers with all mankind. But </div><div class="t m7ac x93 h17 y183 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we must never forget that &quot;in </div><div class="t m7ad x93 h17 y56f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">everything God works for good with </div><div class="t m7ae x93 h17 y185 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">those who love him.&quot; </div><div class="t m66e x58 h17 yb6 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Whatever may be your </div><div class="t m7af x93 h17 ya45 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">circumstances, however dark and </div><div class="t m7b0 x93 h17 y572 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mysterious may be the ways of </div><div class="t m797 x93 h17 ya46 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Providence, though the path may be </div><div class="t m7b1 x93 h17 ya47 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through the deep waters, and trials </div><div class="t m551 x93 h17 y575 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and bereavements may afflict again </div><div class="t m7b2 x93 h17 ya48 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and again, the assurance still comes, </div><div class="t m65d x93 h17 ya49 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&apos;All things work together for good to </div><div class="t m7a3 x93 h17 y576 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them that love God.&apos; (Rom. 8:28).&quot;â€”</div><div class="t m690 x90 h17 ya4a ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Selected Messages, </div><div class="t m54a x6c h17 ya4b ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bk. 2, p. 261. </div><div class="t m65 x93 h19 yc3 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m732 x93 h19 yc7 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. God Feels Our Pain </div><div class="t m7b3 x92 h19 yc9 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 63:9) </div><div class="t m6e3 x93 h19 ycb ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. God&apos;s Presence </div><div class="t m78a x92 h19 ya4c ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 43:2, 3) </div><div class="t m1b5 x93 h19 y57b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. God Helps and Delivers </div><div class="t m4db x92 h19 ya4d ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Ps. 33:18-22) </div><div class="t m7b4 x93 h19 ya4e ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. Helping One Another </div><div class="t m31f x92 h19 yd0 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 Cor. 12:26) </div><div class="t m7b5 x93 h19 y9ca ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. Pain With Courage </div><div class="t m7b6 x92 h19 y4ed ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(2 Cor. 4:8, 9; 1 Cor. 4:11-13) </div><div class="t m7b7 x93 h19 y580 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. Pain Will End </div><div class="t m699 x59 h19 ya4f ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 21:4) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
